videos.description: Sam Hartman scrambles to the outside and finds Alex Bachman, who makes a one-handed touchdown grab in the corner of the end zone.
videos.headline: Wake Forest's Bachman hauls in one-handed TD

videos.description: Tom Flacco finds Sam Gallahan over the middle for a 24-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Flacco connects with Gallahan for Towson TD

videos.description: Demon Deacons WR Greg Dortch reels in Sam Hartman's pass for a 7-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Dortch makes difficult catch for Wake Forest TD

videos.description: Tom Flacco dances in the pocket and finds Shane Simpson in the end zone for an 8-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Flacco dodges defenders, throws TD pass

videos.description: Sam Hartman fakes the handoff and finds a hole to run it in himself.
videos.headline: Wake Forest scores on QB read

videos.description: Greg Dortch hurdles and spins his way into the end zone on a 60-yard punt return TD.
videos.headline: Dortch burns Towson with 2nd punt return TD

videos.description: Tom Flacco connects with Shane Leatherbury for an 18-yard Towson touchdown.
videos.headline: Flacco throws 3rd TD of the day

videos.description: Greg Dortch returns two punts for touchdowns during the second quarter against Towson.
